text: R. R. "Roy" van Aalst (; born 28 March 1983) is a Dutch politician. He has been a member of the House of Representatives representing the Party for Freedom since 23 March 2017 and a member of the States of Overijssel since March 2015."R.R. (Roy) van Aalst" (in Dutch), Parlement & Politiek. Retrieved 15 April 2017. Van Aalst is married, has two children, and lives in Hengelo."Roy van Aalst" (in Dutch), Party for Freedom Overijssel.
